[[File:DSArena.jpg|thumb|right|250px|The proposed combat arena]]
The '''combat arena''' was a proposed addition for the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]]. The site was loved by [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtrooper]] legions for its brutality. The structure contained 100 posts for executions, and 12 enclosed pits for different carnivorous and deadly animals.<ref name="DSD">''[[Death Star Designer]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
[[Leland Chee]] has stated that, while most items, like the [[supercoaster]] and [[Ferris Wheel]] are entered for fun, much of the other information is included in the [[Holocron continuity database]], and is [[canon]]. Regarding the status of the Combat Arena itself, Chee has stated that its best to consider it non-canon unless it resurfaces elsewhere.<ref name="Chee">{{SWBoards|url=thread.jspa?threadID=152583&start=1075#16045442|thread=Holocron continuity database questions|user=[[Leland Chee|Tasty Taste]]|date=2006-12-13|time=4:49 PM}}</ref>

